// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:     March 2011 ANDREW BISHOP
//
// RORO DECK DEFINITION
//
// Changed On   	Changed By  	Reason
// ----------   	----------  	--------------------------------------------------
//02 Apr 2012	cnwrs1		Par 29077 - EDI RORO Stowage Advice errors
