Return Value:		


Date		Who		Reason
24 Aug 2022	navcs2	53899 EUP - SD - VBS MTN - [3] - Maintaining VBS Slot
23 Aug 2023 navhl20 Defect 59936: MTN - Displaying only the first tracked item on the Audit Enquiry for the Vehicle Booking Time Slot
22/03/2024	navcs2	ChangeRequest 61199: EUP | FR | 54329 | VBS - Release Line validation

*/

