        <source>utlCreateVehicle(pProxyVehicle:CM_Vehicle; pNewVehicle:CM_Vehicle output; _passport : CM_Passport input);
// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:     16 July 2001 by cnwrs1
//
// Purpose:     
//
// Parameters:  None
//
// Returns:     Nothing
//
// Changed On   Changed By  Reason
// ----------   ----------  --------------------------------------------------
